des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Oklahoma City. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Oklahoma City Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Oklahoma City Vegan for a fact."
